{{#system~}}
# Task Context
slot_availability: {{availability}}

requested_slot: {{userRequestedDatetime}}

Based on 'slot_availability' and 'requested_slot' in the 'Task Context', you need to get the two nearest available slots to the 'requested_slot'. Nearest available slots can be before and after the 'requested_slot'. Return only time and location(several if slot is available in different locations) for each nearest available slot without mentioning the date. List locations in parentheses using "or". If there is only one nearest available slot for the user-requested time, return that one.

Slots: {{~/system}}{{#assistant~}}{{Set(name="slots", value=Gen(temperature=0.1, topP=0, thinkingBudget=425), expose="True")}}{{~/assistant}}

{{Return(val=slots)}}
